The Peter Schiff Show

Description from the SchiffRadio web site ::

Filling in for Peter is Michael Pento, who will interview Jerry Bowyer, economist and author of the forthcoming Free-Market Capitalist's Survival Guide. <a href="
http://www.jerrybowyer.com" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.jerrybowyer.com</a>

As always, Peter will take your calls on the politics of finance and the economy.




==[Michael Pento will be guest-hosting for Peter the rest of this week]==
